      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKODA LACEY (6) rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early split and gave a sight before being swamped late, finishing a one length fourth at this track over 352m in 19.99. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Should be very hard to beat this time. SHE'S ATHLETIC (7) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Finished in the minors last time when second (19.95) at this track making it back to back placings. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Expected to be in this for a long way. DUAL JEWEL (8) is a last start Mix 5 winner, jumping from this box and scoring by a nose over 352m at this track. Has a very honest record from this same draw, including a win and two minors. Rates a leading chance again.",
